name: He Hasn't Come Back Yet
Lore: '''Princess Leia is wondering about Master Luke...She doesn''t know where he is.'' ''I don''t know where he is.'' ''Nobody knows where he is.''',
Text: 'During your control phase, target any character alone at one of your exterior planet sites (except a docking bay). Draw destiny. Target is missing if destiny + 3 > ability.',
